SUMMARY:Event Frontmatter Spec
DESCRIPTION:Any post on this site can become a calendar event by adding tags = ['event'] and the required frontmatter below.\nResults Event partial — rendered at the top of the page with &ldquo;Download event&rdquo; and &ldquo;Subscribe to calendar&rdquo; buttons; location is linked if a URL Per-event .ics — generated at build time, downloadable at /{page-path}/event.ics Main calendar feed — https://cyborg.support/event.ics aggregates all events; subscribe once in Apple Calendar, Google Calendar, or any iCal client and get all future events automatically Required These fields are needed to generate a valid .ics entry.\n
URL:https://cyborg.support/site/event/
LOCATION:https://zoom.us/j/cyborg-support
ORGANIZER;CN=Cyborg Support:MAILTO:noreply@cyborg.support
END:VEVENT
